definition: square/frame/rule/(legal) case/style/character/standard/pattern/(grammar) case/(classical) to obstruct/to hinder/(classical) to arrive/to come/(classical) to investigate/to study exhaustively
to be entitled/to qualify/to be qualified

sentences.english: Scholarships will be canceled for those who cannot pass the health examination.
sentences.chinese: 入学体检不合格者，奖学金资格将被取消。

sentences.english: The authors are eminently qualified to explore the topic.
sentences.chinese: 这两位作者非常有资格探讨这一主题。

sentences.english: They qualified for the qualifying tourney by their finish in last year's regional tournaments.
sentences.chinese: 他们通过去年的地区选拔赛获得了落选锦标赛的资格。

sentences.english: Lettered words has the qualifications to enter Chinese dictionary.
sentences.chinese: 字母词有资格进入汉语词典。

sentences.english: At least hold accountant certificate specialize in accounting or budget.
sentences.chinese: 拥有会计师或预算师资格。

sentences.english: I've obtained a Senior Bartender's Qualification Certificate.
sentences.chinese: 我获得了高级调酒师资格证书。

sentences.english: Article 6 Anyone who wants to obtain a qualification of lawyers shall pass the uniform national judicial examination.
sentences.chinese: 第六条取得律师资格应当经过国家统一的司法考试。

sentences.english: The wolf and the sheep are not qualified to talk about freedom.
sentences.chinese: 狼和羊都没有资格谈论自由。

sentences.english: Strength alone knows conficts, weakness is below even defeat , and is born vanquished.
sentences.chinese: 弱者甚至连失败都不够资格，而是生来就是被征服的。

sentences.english: Labor and Social Security Department Director of the Center for Occupational accreditation Chen told reporters.
sentences.chinese: 劳动和社会保障部中心主任陈职业资格认证对记者说。

sentences.english: Do I qualify for the scholarship to England?
sentences.chinese: 我符合留英奖学金的资格吗？

sentences.english: Once the student drops out, he or she will be disqualified from the programme.
sentences.chinese: 受助学生一旦辍学，其受助资格将会自动取消。

sentences.english: Will travel overseas affect eligibility under the new requirements?
sentences.chinese: 根据新的要求，海外旅行是否会影响入籍资格？

sentences.english: Applicants presenting International Baccalaureate diplomas are eligible for general admission to the University.
sentences.chinese: 申请人提交国际文凭文凭一般大学入学资格。

sentences.english: Article 2 The system of uniform national examination shall be applied to the qualification examination on customs declarers .
sentences.chinese: 第二条报关员资格考试实行全国统一考试制度。
